N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 303.5 - Filing date

State Regulations

On the day the Administrator receives the prescribed filing
fee, the Administrator shall date stamp the request for arbitration form. Such
date shall be considered the filing date. Notes
